<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>まるヨガ（MARU YOGA）| 愛媛県新居浜市 古典・ハタヨガ</title>
  <meta name="description" content="愛媛県新居浜市のまるヨガ（MARU YOGA）。インストラクター金丸良子による古典・ハタヨガクラス。14年のキャリアを持つ講師が少人数でていねいに指導します。体験クラス随時受付中。">
  <meta property="og:title" content="まるヨガ（MARU YOGA）| 新居浜市の古典・ハタヨガ">
  <meta property="og:description" content="愛媛県新居浜市のまるヨガ。古典・ハタヨガクラス。体験クラス随時受付中。">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --green-deep:  #2d5a3d;
      --green-mid:   #4a7c59;
      --green-light: #7aab88;
      --green-pale:  #e8f4eb;
      --green-bg:    #f4faf5;
      --cream:       #fdfaf6;
      --text:        #2c2c2c;
      --text-sub:    #555;
      --radius:      12px;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* ── ヘッダー ── */
    header {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(253,250,246,.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dde8de;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .logo-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1.2; }
    .logo-en {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--green-deep); letter-spacing: .08em;
    }
    .logo-jp { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--green-mid); letter-spacing: .12em; }
    nav a {
      color: var(--green-deep); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 500;
      padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--green-mid);
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    nav a:hover { background: var(--green-mid); color: white; }

    /* ── ヒーロー ── */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--green-deep) 0%, var(--green-mid) 60%, #6fa87a 100%);
      color: white; text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 24px 64px;
    }
    .hero-leaf { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
    .hero-en {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 7vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .15em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .hero-jp { font-size: 1.05rem; letter-spacing: .2em; opacity: .85; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero-copy {
      font-size: .95rem; opacity: .9; max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.9;
    }
    .hero-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white; color: var(--green-deep);
      font-weight: 700; font-size: .92rem;
      padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 28px;
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: .05em;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
      transition: transform .2s;
    }
    .hero-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* ── セクション共通 ── */
    section { padding: 64px 24px; }
    .container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--green-deep);
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .sec-title::after {
      content: ''; display: block;
      width: 40px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--green-light);
      margin: 10px auto 32px;
    }
    .sec-lead { text-align: center; color: var(--text-sub); font-size: .93rem; margin-bottom: 32px; }

    /* ── コンセプト ── */
    .concept { background: var(--green-bg); }
    .concept-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px; margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .concept-card {
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px 22px; text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08);
    }
    .concept-ico { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
    .concept-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .concept-card p { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.75; }

    /* ── インストラクター ── */
    .instructor-card {
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 32px 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08);
      display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .instructor-icon {
      width: 80px; height: 80px; flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--green-pale);
      border-radius: 50%; display: flex;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .instructor-name {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .instructor-role { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--green-mid); margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: .06em; }
    .instructor-bio { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* ── クラス・スケジュール ── */
    .classes { background: var(--green-bg); }
    .class-table {
      width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08);
    }
    .class-table th {
      background: var(--green-deep); color: white;
      padding: 12px 16px; font-size: .88rem;
      font-weight: 600; text-align: left;
    }
    .class-table td {
      padding: 14px 16px; font-size: .88rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--green-pale);
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .class-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .class-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: var(--green-bg); }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .badge-green { background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green-deep); }
    .badge-orange { background: #fff3e0; color: #e65100; }
    .notice-box {
      background: var(--green-pale);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--green-mid);
      border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
      padding: 16px 20px; margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: .87rem; color: var(--green-deep); line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* ── 料金 ── */
    .price-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .price-card {
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px 22px; text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08);
      border-top: 4px solid var(--green-light);
      position: relative;
    }
    .price-card.featured { border-top-color: var(--green-deep); }
    .price-tag {
      position: absolute; top: -1px; right: 16px;
      background: var(--green-deep); color: white;
      font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    .price-card h3 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .price-amount {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-deep);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .price-unit { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--text-sub); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .price-note { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* ── アクセス ── */
    .access { background: var(--green-bg); }
    .access-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .access-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .access-info {
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08);
    }
    .access-info h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .access-row {
      display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: .87rem; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .access-ico { flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .access-row a { color: var(--green-mid); }
    .map-wrap {
      border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08);
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    }
    .map-wrap iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; }

    /* ── お問い合わせ ── */
    .contact-box {
      background: var(--green-deep); color: white;
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 40px 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-box h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .contact-box p { font-size: .88rem; opacity: .85; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.8; }
    .contact-tel {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: block;
    }
    .contact-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white; color: var(--green-deep);
      font-weight: 700; font-size: .9rem;
      padding: 11px 28px; border-radius: 24px;
      text-decoration: none; margin: 4px;
      transition: transform .2s;
    }
    .contact-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .contact-btn.outline {
      background: transparent; color: white;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6);
    }

    /* ── cafe nora バナー ── */
    .cafe-banner {
      background: #fdf6ec;
      border: 1.5px solid #e8d5b0;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 20px 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .cafe-banner-txt h4 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; color: #5a3e1b; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .cafe-banner-txt p { font-size: .82rem; color: #7a5c2a; }
    .cafe-banner-btn {
      background: #8b6230; color: white;
      padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 20px;
      text-decoration: none; font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap; transition: opacity .2s;
    }
    .cafe-banner-btn:hover { opacity: .85; }

    /* ── フッター ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--green-deep); color: white;
      text-align: center; padding: 36px 24px;
    }
    footer .f-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; letter-spacing: .1em; margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    footer .f-sub { font-size: .8rem; opacity: .65; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); font-size: .82rem; margin: 0 8px; text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: white; }
    footer .f-copy { font-size: .75rem; opacity: .45; margin-top: 16px; }

    /* ── レイアウト切り替えタブ ── */
    .ls-header { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .ls-header .sec-title { text-align:left; margin-bottom:0; }
    .ls-header .sec-title::after { margin:8px 0 0; }
    .ls-switcher { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; }
    .ls-switcher span { font-size:.78rem; color:var(--text-sub); }
    .ls-btn {
      padding:7px 18px; border-radius:20px;
      border:1.5px solid var(--green-mid);
      background:white; color:var(--green-mid);
      font-size:.84rem; font-weight:600;
      cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s; white-space:nowrap;
    }
    .ls-btn.active, .ls-btn:hover { background:var(--green-deep); color:white; border-color:var(--green-deep); }
    .ls-content { animation:lsFade .25s ease; }
    @keyframes lsFade { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(6px); } to { opacity:1; transform:none; } }

    /* ── 案①：会場別カード ── */
    .venue-card { background:white; border-radius:var(--radius); overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08); margin-bottom:14px; }
    .venue-header { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; padding:14px 20px; color:white; }
    .venue-icon { font-size:1.5rem; flex-shrink:0; }
    .venue-name { font-weight:700; font-size:.97rem; }
    .venue-addr { font-size:.74rem; opacity:.82; margin-top:2px; }
    .sch-table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; }
    .sch-table tr:not(:last-child) td { border-bottom:1px solid var(--green-pale); }
    .sch-day { padding:12px 16px; font-size:.84rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--green-deep); white-space:nowrap; width:90px; }
    .sch-time { padding:12px 8px; font-size:.83rem; color:var(--text-sub); white-space:nowrap; width:115px; }
    .sch-name { padding:12px 16px 12px 4px; font-size:.88rem; }
    .stag { display:inline-block; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:10px; font-size:.7rem; font-weight:700; margin-left:6px; vertical-align:middle; }
    .stag-zoom { background:#e3f2fd; color:#1565c0; }
    .stag-min { background:var(--green-pale); color:var(--green-deep); }
    .stag-notice { background:#fff3e0; color:#e65100; }
    .stag-irr { background:#f3e5f5; color:#6a1b9a; }

    /* ── 案②：週間グリッド ── */
    .week-scroll { overflow-x:auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch; }
    .week-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(7,minmax(100px,1fr)); gap:8px; min-width:700px; }
    .wg-col { }
    .wg-head {
      background:var(--green-deep); color:white;
      text-align:center; padding:9px 4px;
      font-weight:700; font-size:.9rem;
      border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .wg-head.rest { background:#bbb; }
    .wg-rest-label { text-align:center; padding:16px 4px; font-size:.78rem; color:#aaa; font-style:italic; }
    .wg-block {
      border-radius:6px; padding:9px 10px; margin-top:6px;
      font-size:.75rem; line-height:1.55; color:white;
    }
    .wg-time { font-weight:700; font-size:.72rem; opacity:.9; }
    .wg-name { font-weight:600; margin-top:1px; }
    .wg-venue { opacity:.75; font-size:.68rem; margin-top:2px; }
    .wg-irr { opacity:.75; }
    .wg-s { background:var(--green-mid); }
    .wg-s.wg-irr { background:var(--green-light); }
    .wg-t { background:#8d6e63; }
    .wg-c { background:#3d7ab5; }
    .wg-e { background:#7b5ea7; }
    .wg-legend { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:16px; justify-content:center; }
    .wg-leg { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; padding:4px 14px; border-radius:12px; font-size:.78rem; font-weight:600; color:white; }

    /* ── 案③：曜日別リスト ── */
    .dl-wrap { background:white; border-radius:var(--radius); overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(45,90,61,.08); }
    .dl-row { display:flex; align-items:stretch; border-bottom:1px solid var(--green-pale); }
    .dl-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    .dl-day {
      width:52px; flex-shrink:0;
      background:var(--green-deep); color:white;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      font-weight:700; font-size:1.05rem;
    }
    .dl-inner { flex:1; }
    .dl-class { display:flex; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; padding:12px 20px; border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    .dl-class:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    .dl-time { font-size:.82rem; color:var(--text-sub); white-space:nowrap; min-width:110px; }
    .dl-name { font-size:.9rem; font-weight:600; flex:1; min-width:120px; }
    .dl-vtag { font-size:.73rem; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px; font-weight:700; white-space:nowrap; }
    .dl-vs { background:var(--green-pale); color:var(--green-deep); }
    .dl-vt { background:#f3ede8; color:#7d6248; }
    .dl-vc { background:#e3f2fd; color:#1565c0; }
    .dl-ve { background:#f3e5f5; color:#6a1b9a; }

    /* ── レスポンシブ ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .instructor-card { flex-direction: column; }
      .instructor-icon { margin: 0 auto; }
      .sch-day { width:70px; padding:10px 10px; }
      .sch-time { width:95px; }
      .dl-time { min-width:90px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ヘッダー -->
<header>
  <div class="logo-wrap">
    <span class="logo-en">MARU YOGA</span>
    <span class="logo-jp">まるヨガ</span>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <a href="../index.html">cafe nora へ →</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- ヒーロー -->
<div class="hero">
  <span class="hero-leaf">🌿</span>
  <h1 class="hero-en">MARU YOGA</h1>
  <p class="hero-jp">ま る ヨ ガ</p>
  <p class="hero-copy">
    小さなスタジオで、<br>
    呼吸と向き合う時間を。<br>
    新居浜市の古典・ハタヨガクラス
  </p>
  <a href="#contact" class="hero-btn">お問い合わせ・ご質問はこちら</a>
</div>

<!-- ★ リアントゥール 告知バナー（最上部） -->
<div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a3a2a 0%,#2d5a3d 50%,#3d7a52 100%); color:white; padding:0;">
  <div style="max-width:860px; margin:0 auto; padding:36px 24px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:24px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div>
      <p style="font-size:.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.18em; opacity:.7; margin-bottom:8px; text-transform:uppercase;">毎月開催 ／ Special Event</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif; font-size:clamp(1.3rem,4vw,1.9rem); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.08em; margin-bottom:8px; line-height:1.3;">
        出張ヨガ × ランチ<br>
        <span style="font-size:.75em; opacity:.85;">at リアントゥール</span>
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size:.88rem; opacity:.85; line-height:1.8; max-width:420px;">
        素敵な結婚式場でヨガを楽しみ、その後ランチも。<br>
        <strong style="color:#a8d5b5;">次回：2026年 5月 23日（土）10:30〜</strong>　参加費 3,500円
      </p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; flex-shrink:0;">
      <a href="liantour.html"
        style="display:block; background:white; color:#2d5a3d; font-weight:700; font-size:.9rem; padding:13px 28px; border-radius:28px; text-decoration:none; text-align:center; box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.25); transition:transform .2s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='none'">
        🌿 イベント詳細・写真を見る
      </a>
      <a href="yoyaku.html"
        style="display:block; background:rgba(255,255,255,.18); color:white; font-size:.85rem; padding:10px 28px; border-radius:28px; text-decoration:none; text-align:center; border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.5); transition:background .2s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,.3)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,.18)'">
        🌿 リアントゥールヨガの予約はこちら
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- コンセプト -->
<section class="concept">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="sec-title">まるヨガについて</h2>
    <p class="sec-lead">心と体をていねいに整える、少人数制のヨガクラスです</p>
    <div class="concept-grid">
      <div class="concept-card">
        <span class="concept-ico">🧘</span>
        <h3>古典・ハタヨガ</h3>
        <p>ポーズ（アーサナ）と呼吸（プラーナーヤーマ）を中心とした伝統的なヨガ。ゆっくりと体を動かしながら、内側に意識を向けます。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-card">
        <span class="concept-ico">🌱</span>
        <h3>初心者大歓迎</h3>
        <p>「体が硬いから」「運動が苦手だから」は関係ありません。どんな体の状態からでも、その方に合わせてクラスを進めます。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-card">
        <span class="concept-ico">🏡</span>
        <h3>小さなスタジオ</h3>
        <p>14年前にガレージを改装した温かみのある空間。木の質感と自然光に包まれた、居心地のよい場所でクラスを行います。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

